Continuing the \href{https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/explication}{explication}
of the IPARX identity\index{IPARX identity},
one piece or facet of resource intensity of the economy~\Rparen{}
is the primary energy intensity\index{primary energy intensity}~\REpparen{} of the world economy.
\REp{} is the amount of primary energy\index{primary energy} required to create one unit (dollar) of
